{"tid":991812,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"依家嘅你係生活定係生存？","createTime":"2019-01-22T16:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T01:24:29.000Z","uid":104232,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2be90ac49b2cdf444bea44a4695d8abd12dd7436","tid":991812,"uid":104232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:09:06.000Z","msg":"有無人會間唔中諗下自己呢一刻<br />\n做既野 讀既書 返既工 係咪自己鐘意<br />\n返左一年半既工 咩野都得唔到 <br />\n由一開始對未來好有盼望 <br />\n到依家見唔到未來 而自己只係一個平凡既打工仔<br />\n一份人工做兩個人既野 senior又唔睇好 <br />\n<br />\n從前細個會好唔鐘意一班扮哂野既成年人<br />\n但原來大個左先知呢班扮哂野既人 <br />\n先可以係社會到生存到 <br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3812ae3180754146465ef8d0a678c85a198bab93","tid":991812,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"你細細個已經知大人扮緊野<br />\n其實已經唔錯"},{"pid":"4ef3b127fb52c7baa422b7ad398fe9a8e83d2d3b","tid":991812,"uid":104232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3812ae3180754146465ef8d0a678c85a198bab93","tid":991812,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"你細細個已經知大人扮緊野<br />\n其實已經唔錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:15:04.000Z","msg":"想變返細路仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b6adff7227f2f6c5185e8a8556eccd54ea027c","tid":991812,"uid":196240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"生存 為左係香港生存 揀份高人工既工做 而放棄夢想"},{"pid":"7f3e500113bdb4daa577dc63c86475865472fc3f","tid":991812,"uid":104232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91b6adff7227f2f6c5185e8a8556eccd54ea027c","tid":991812,"uid":196240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"生存 為左係香港生存 揀份高人工既工做 而放棄夢想"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"Same here 人工雖然唔太高 但餓自己唔死 <br />\n係香港談夢想談何容易"},{"pid":"784373baf33d226b0a52e6a9de7c7892453af08b","tid":991812,"uid":196240,"like":0,"dislike"